A [[currency_exchange]] site serving those purchasing bitcoins using Euro (EUR) sent as cash-in-the-mail.

The exchange bases their price on current market price from the [[MtGox]] and adds a small trading fee on top.

Before sending, review the terms of service to help prevent losing your funds.

The service was announced July 11, 2012 (1.1).

